          "description": "This unit cannot be defeated by damage from Burn status effects. This unit is not affected by stun effects and cannot be sent to the reinforcements from the battlefield.\n\nWhenever there are 3 or more burning allies on the battlefield, this unit will survive any attack that would defeat this unit with 1HP.\n\nEach time this unit gets the turn, all allies will heal for 30% of their max HP.\n\nAt the end of each of this unit's turns:\n- If this unit has a Power Charge, all allies will become Enraged, then the Power Charge is removed from this unit.\n- Otherwise, this unit will gain a Power Charge.\n\nAn Enraged unit's attack is increased to 1.5x until the end of their next turn. Enrage will overwrite any existing Weak or Enrage effects on affected units. Power Charges cannot stack and will be removed when the user leaves the battlefield."
        }
